data.description: On offer is one of the a stunning four level Victorian townhome located in Butchers Hill and just across from Patterson Park's north west corner. The home's location allows for some stunning views of Patterson Park and the southeast waterfront to the south.  The end-of-group position of this home allows for plenty of windows. The southern and eastern exposure of the home affords plenty of natural light in everyone of this homes rooms. Everything inside has been custom built and of the highest quality of materials rarely seen in homes in this price range. All trim, crown molding, baseboards, doors, etc. are of solid hardwoods. Door hardware of solid brass accentuates the high quality of the wood.
